OL,3,CNorth West MP urges curbs on noisy
OL,4,Cfireworks
OL,6,FA North West MP has launched a
OL,7,Fcampaign to curb loud fireworks saying
OL,8,Fthey distress large numbers of people
OL,9,Fwith medical conditions, anxiety or
OL,10,Fpast experience of war zones.
OL,12,FYasmin Qureshi, Labour MP for Bolton,
OL,13,Fhas brought a ten minute rule bill to
OL,14,Fthe Commons today trying to change the
OL,15,Flaw around fireworks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
