OL,3,CNorth West MP urges curbs on noisy
OL,4,Cfireworks
OL,6,FShe added that research points to
OL,7,Falmost half of people surveyed want
OL,8,Fprivate backyard displays banned and a
OL,9,Ffurther third want tighter
OL,10,Frestrictions.
OL,12,FShe said: "One family told me their
OL,13,Fautistic son becomes extremely
OL,14,Fdistressed by unexpected fireworks. He
OL,15,Fscreams, hides and cannot settle for
OL,16,Fhours. They want him to enjoy
OL,17,Fcelebrations like any other child, but
OL,18,Funpredictable late-night fireworks
OL,19,Fmake evenings frightening rather than
OL,20,Fjoyful."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
