OL,3,CNorth West MP urges curbs on noisy
OL,4,Cfireworks
OL,6,FBut Ms Qureshi says this is not a call
OL,7,Ffor a blanket ban, organised displays
OL,8,Fare less of a problem because people
OL,9,Fknow they are happening and can
OL,10,Fprepare.
OL,12,F"The real problem is unpredictable
OL,13,Ffireworks set off in neighbourhoods.
OL,14,FThey are sudden, loud and impossible
OL,15,Fto anticipate. Families can prepare
OL,16,Ffor a display at eight o'clock in a
OL,17,Fpark. They cannot prepare for an
OL,18,Fexplosion outside their window at half
OL,19,Fpast midnight".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
