OL,3,CNorth West MP urges curbs on noisy
OL,4,Cfireworks
OL,6,FAccording to the Bolton MP the
OL,7,Fveterans support organisation Combat
OL,8,FStress reports a 25% increase in calls
OL,9,Fat this time of year. She said they
OL,10,Fwant a review of current rules,
OL,11,Fclearer safety information, and limits
OL,12,Fon when fireworks can be sold and used.
OL,14,FThe Bill would introduce a maximum
OL,15,Fnoise limit, with clear labelling and
OL,16,Fnew powers for local authorities to
OL,17,Ftackle sales.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
