OL,3,CNorth West MP urges curbs on noisy
OL,4,Cfireworks
OL,6,FYasmin Qureshi concluded by saying
OL,7,F"People do not want fireworks banned.
OL,8,FThey want celebrations to continue.
OL,9,FBut they want the loudest fireworks
OL,10,Fused safely and predictably and with
OL,11,Frespect for neighbours.
OL,13,FThey want their families, pets, and
OL,14,Fvulnerable neighbours to feel safe in
OL,15,Ftheir homes. They want councils to
OL,16,Fhave the ability to act. And they want
OL,17,Ffireworks sold responsibly and clearly
OL,18,Flabelled.
OL,20,FThis Bill offers a balanced,
OL,21,Fpractical, and fair way forward".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
